From 37d4a21bee034d226c5718cd8427c8d90f8a5078 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Zach Taylor <zctaylor.work@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 5 Jun 2026 00:30:21 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 46/48] Adapt overlay patches to upstream sync (AIClient trait,
 Dropdown PartialEq)

Upstream 03ad9ea9 (216 commits) changed APIs our patches use: the AIClient trait gained 11 methods and list_agents dropped its repo param, so GrpcBridgeAIClient delegates the new ones to inner; Dropdown<T> now requires T: PartialEq, so BackendAction and GrpcHarnessAction derive it; SpawnAgentRequest.prompt is now Option<String>; AmbientAgentTask gained a run_time field. cargo check -p warp --lib passes.
